Documentation is stored in data/doc/ruby/Borges.  It will be installed
into the data dir (/usr/local/share or similar).

QUICK START

Assumes that Ruby is installed in paths under /usr/local.

Install:

  $ ./setup.rb config
  $ ./setup.rb setup
  $ sudo ./setup.rb install

Start:

  $ ruby /usr/local/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/Borges/WEBrick.rb

Use:

  Open http://localhost:7000/borges/counter in your favorite web browser.

